21
00:01:01,500 --> 00:01:04,166
[Spider-Man] Look at them
down there. I'll bet each one
has somebody close.

22
00:01:04,166 --> 00:01:05,583
I feel so distant.

23
00:01:05,583 --> 00:01:07,625
